    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Pleurothallis sabanillae. A. Habit. B. Flower. C. Dissected perianth. D. Ovary, column and lip in lateral view. E. Lip adaxial and abaxial views. Illustration by L. Vélez-Abarca based on the type." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8243239/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8243241>
